WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:03.270
MAN Truck &amp; Bus AG, Teststrecke Munich

00:00:03.270 --> 00:00:05.600
As a trainee at MAN you have a lot of possibilities. 

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:08.800
There are lots of events and we spend a lot of time together. 

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:13.000
You even get the chance to drive a truck or a bus on your own. 

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:13.900
And that's what we did today.

00:00:27.120 --> 00:00:28.120
Well, let's go then. 

00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:34.120
The truck is 17 meters long.

00:00:38.300 --> 00:00:40.000
Great Feeling!

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:45.120
It's long and heavy. Slightly different than my Polo.

00:00:51.170 --> 00:00:57.190
It doesn't really feel that fast. First time in a truck and first time driving one.

00:00:57.190 --> 00:00:58.810
Wow.

00:00:58.810 --> 00:01:01.120
The bus is pretty long.

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:04.800
Crazy. Totally crazy. But in a good way.

00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:13.720
You can feel the tons of weight you're moving. 

00:01:13.720 --> 00:01:15.120
Definitely a great feeling. 

00:01:40.490 --> 00:01:44.300
I'm a trainee at EC in the area of engineering. 

00:01:44.300 --> 00:01:49.300
And I can now experience what I normally see in 3D animations or on drawings.

00:01:49.300 --> 00:01:55.420
I'm a trainee at quality management. Events like that are awesome.

00:01:55.420 --> 00:01:57.120
A welcome change of ways.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:03.860
Events like today are that extra something.

00:02:03.860 --> 00:02:09.760
I think it's thrilling that to be experiencing our products at first hand.

00:02:09.760 --> 00:02:13.040
Great Day! Seen the products in action! Ace!

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:16.280
Super. So much fun, didn't expect that.

00:02:16.280 --> 00:02:19.380
Summing up: A great experience.

00:02:19.380 --> 00:02:21.120
Very good. A dream come true.

